title: [Snyk] Fix for 1 vulnerabilities
body:
#### Description
This PR fixes one or more vulnerable packages in the `npm` dependencies of this project.
See the [Snyk test report](https://app.snyk.io/org/william1998/test/github/d03c8147-1bbf-4cf4-935a-1b931f4bacb6/master..snyk-fix-d2e6a4d6c1ba2d787408a46fcbcd6a03) for more details.

#### Snyk Project: [William1998/PrescriptPal:package.json](https://app.snyk.io/org/william1998/project/d03c8147-1bbf-4cf4-935a-1b931f4bacb6)
#### Snyk Organization: [William1998](https://app.snyk.io/org/william1998)


#### Changes included in this PR

- Changes to the following files to upgrade the vulnerable dependencies to a fixed version:
    - package.json
    - package-lock.json



#### Vulnerabilities that will be fixed
##### With an upgrade:
- [SNYK-JS-MONGODB-473855](https://snyk.io/vuln/SNYK-JS-MONGODB-473855)




You can read more about Snyk's upgrade and patch logic in [Snyk's documentation](https://snyk.io/docs/using-snyk/).

Check the changes in this PR to ensure they won't cause issues with your project.

Stay secure,
The Snyk team
